YaY - Yet another YARM
======================

YaY is a (web)radio manager suite, providing the ability to create channel schedules,
automatically capture live shows, publish all shows to the archive, provide multi-
faceted search and make it easy for content creators to upload or stream their
contributions. It builds upon the liquidsoap streaming backend software, which
interfaces with any icecast/shoutcast compatible client and server.

Dependencies
============
php5 (+mongo +id3 +vorbis +fileinfo)
mongodb
sox

Config
======

max_file_upload_size in php.ini
